Class TreeTransient<I extends Serializable,M extends TreeTransient>

java.lang.Object
com.pineframework.core.datamodel.model.FlatTransient<I>
com.pineframework.core.datamodel.model.TreeTransient<I,M>
Type Parameters:
I - the type of identity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Transient<I>, Serializable
public abstract class TreeTransient<I extends Serializable,M extends TreeTransient> extends FlatTransient<I>
All models such as value objects, data transfer object (DTO), etc should be extended from AbstractTransient. AbstractTransient implements equals and hash code and also toString method.
